# Environment Variables

## Required Variables

MONGO_URL=your_mongodb_connection_string
SECRET_KEY=your_jwt_secret_key

## Optional Variables

PORT=5000
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000

## Example MongoDB Connection Strings

# Local MongoDB
MONGO_URL=mongodb://localhost:27017/school-management

# MongoDB Atlas
MONGO_URL=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/school-management?retryWrites=true&w=majority

## Security Notes

- Never commit this file to version control
- Use strong, random values for SECRET_KEY
- Keep your MongoDB credentials secure
- Update FRONTEND_URL for production deployment
